520
00:32:17.062 --> 00:32:19.523
Go fuck yourself. You got me fired.

521
00:32:19.606 --> 00:32:22.067
All it takes is one phone call.

522
00:32:22.150 --> 00:32:23.151
Think about it.

523
00:32:25.070 --> 00:32:29.575
Cool. So. uh. what kind of. uh.
cash and prizes are you gonna offer me?

524
00:32:30.993 --> 00:32:33.245
